</p><p>The <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eigenvector" class=3D"m=
w-redirect" title=3D"Eigenvector">eigenvectors</a> of <span class=3D"texhtm=
l mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;"><b>A</b></span> are the principal axes=
