lue" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Eigenvalue">eigenvalues</a> of <span cl=
ass=3D"texhtml mvar" style=3D"font-style:italic;"><b>A</b></span> are the r=
eciprocals of the squares of the semi-axes (in three dimensions these are <=
span class=3D"texhtml"><i>a</i><sup>=E2=88=922</sup></span>, <span class=3D=
